<i>noun</i>: 하객 [하ː객], 투숙객 [투숙깩], 축하객 [추카객], 손님 [손님], 손 [손], 내빈 [내ː빈], 고객 [고객], 게스트 [], 객 [객] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>하객 [하ː객]</dt><br>
<dd>guest; visitor</dd><br>
<dd>축하해 주러 온 손님.</dd><br>
<dd>A person coming to congratulate someone on a certain event.</dd><br>
<dt>투숙객 [투숙깩]</dt><br>
<dd>guest; lodger</dd><br>
<dd>여관, 호텔 등의 숙박 시설에서 묵는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who stays in such lodging facilities as an inn, a hotel, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>축하객 [추카객]</dt><br>
<dd>guest; visitor</dd><br>
<dd>축하하기 위해 온 손님.</dd><br>
<dd>A person coming to congratulate someone on a certain event.</dd><br>
<dt>손님 [손님]</dt><br>
<dd>1. visitor; caller; guest</dd><br>
<dd>(높임말로) 다른 곳에서 찾아온 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(honorific) A person who comes to visit someone.</dd><br>
<dd>2. guest; customer</dd><br>
<dd>(높임말로) 여관이나 음식점 등의 가게에 찾아온 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>(honorific) A person who visits an inn, restaurant, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. guest</dd><br>
<dd>결혼식이나 장례식 등에 참석하러 온 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who comes to attend a wedding, funeral, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>4. visitor</dd><br>
<dd>공연이나 전시회 등을 구경하러 온 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who comes to see a performance, exhibition, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>5. passenger</dd><br>
<dd>버스나 택시 등과 같은 교통수단을 이용하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who uses a means of transportation such as a bus, taxi, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>손 [손]</dt><br>
<dd>1. guest</dd><br>
<dd>다른 곳에서 찾아온 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who is visiting from somewhere else.</dd><br>
<dd>2. guest; customer; patron</dd><br>
<dd>여관이나 음식점 등의 가게에 찾아온 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who visits a business such as an inn, restaurant, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>내빈 [내ː빈]</dt><br>
<dd>guest</dd><br>
<dd>식장이나 공식적인 모임에 초대를 받고 온 손님.</dd><br>
<dd>A person coming to a ceremony or official meeting by invitation.</dd><br>
<dt>고객 [고객]</dt><br>
<dd>customer; guest; patron; client; clientele</dd><br>
<dd>상품을 사거나 서비스를 이용하는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who buys products or uses services.</dd><br>
<dt>게스트 []</dt><br>
<dd>guest</dd><br>
<dd>방송 프로그램에 초대되어 나오는 사람.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who appears on a broadcast show on invitation.</dd><br>
<dt>객 [객]</dt><br>
<dd>visitor; guest</dd><br>
<dd>찾아온 손님.</dd><br>
<dd>A person who visits.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>